    The Past Doctor Adventures features new adventures of the first seven Doctors, with the following exceptions: 
    -- <em>Scream of the Shalka</em>, a novelisation of a webcast story featuring the Alternative Ninth Doctor; 
    -- <em>The Infinity Doctors</em>, featuring an unspecified Doctor;
    -- <em>The Face of the Enemy</em>, featuring The Master;
    -- <em>Fear Itself</em>, the only PDA featuring the Eighth Doctor.

